    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/stable/linux.git/commit/?id=10feb428a5045d5eb18a5d755fbb8f0cc9645626">https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/stable/linux.git/commit/?id=10feb428a5045d5eb18a5d755fbb8f0cc9645626</a></p>

<p><a href="https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/stable/linux.git/commit/?id=d34ac51b76e8c7de6094cfb11780ef9c2b93469f">https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/stable/linux.git/commit/?id=d34ac51b76e8c7de6094cfb11780ef9c2b93469f</a></p>

