    <title type="html"><![CDATA[vpn]]></title>
    <link href="http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2020/09/10/kernel-vpn/"/>
    <updated>2020-09-10T04:39:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2020/09/10/kernel-vpn</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>方案一</h3>

<p>client &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;> hongkong &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-> server<br/>
           xor/drop      squid</p>

<h3>方案二</h3>

<p>client &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;> guangzhou &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-> hongkong &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-> server<br/>
          xor/drop       squid      xor/drop/icmp+mss    squid</p>

<p><a href="http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/cats/tools~squid/">squid</a></p>

<p><a href="http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2020/07/09/kernel-tcp-icmp/">icmp</a></p>

<p><a href="http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2020/07/09/kernel-adjust-mss/">mss</a></p>

<p><a href="http://abcdxyzk.github.io/blog/2020/09/10/kernel-digest-xor/">xor</a></p>

<p>drop: 丢弃异常reset、fin等包</p>
]]></content>
